---
title: Mumbai White Fish & Cauliflower Curry with Garlic Rice & Coriander
description: Dive into bold Mumbai-inspired flavours with this creamy, spiced fish and cauliflower curry! Paired with fragrant garlic rice and a sprinkle of fresh coriander, it’s a warm, comforting bowl with a little kick and a lot of soul.

